accomplishment_projects.title: Mobile Application
accomplishment_projects.description: It demontrates my ability to create custom animated components to fulfill complicated requirements and the experience of managing an iOS app in DEV, UAT and PROD environment.

accomplishment_projects.title: Event Time Confirmation System
accomplishment_projects.description: This project attempts to confirm times available to all members of an event on a weekly basis.

accomplishment_projects.title: Translate Pytorch Model and Weight into Libtorch Model for C++ Project
accomplishment_projects.description: This project is a complete C++ translation of mediapipe's blazeface from python. The goal is to integrate existing pytorch model into desktop application using C++and imgui.

accomplishment_projects.title: Deploy Custom Pytorch Model to Web Frontend
accomplishment_projects.description: This project attempts to deploy a custom trained model (trained in pytorch) into the browser.

accomplishment_projects.title: Defect Classifcation by Object Detections
accomplishment_projects.description: We implement a defect classifier by means of object detection.

accomplishment_projects.title: Text Detection and Text Removal for Signboards
accomplishment_projects.description: Implemented a text detection as well as an inpainting module to erase the text on signboards.

accomplishment_projects.title: DefectGAN - a Synthetic Data Generation Model
accomplishment_projects.description: A GAN model that generates defect data for object detection model. I have implemented the model from scratch according to the description in the paper in frameworks (pytorch and tensorflow).

accomplishment_projects.title: Dictionary App with Next.js and Electron.js
accomplishment_projects.description: Second trial of building dictionary desktop app using electron and next.js.

recommendations:
Juno Ng



I worked with James in the Stand Overflow project and was very impressed by his ability to quickly learn and adopt new technologies. James has solid background in mathematics and that is reflected in the clarity of his code. He has acquired the knowledge on Ethereum blockchain and the ability to write smart contract with solidity through the project. I would highly recommend James to those who need an employee who is not only self-driven but also a quick learner.
